data.description: Welcome home to this huge 5 bedroom 5 bathroom + office property located in the highly sought after Estates at Tradition.  As soon as you enter, you immediately notice the abundant natural light and view of the pool.  Soaring high ceilings throughout the home with beautiful trim work.  The downstairs living areas boast diagonal tile flooring and neutral paint colors.  Triple split bedroom floor plan on the first floor for added privacy with an additional bonus/office room next to the primary suite.  The home features a large dining area, formal living room with fireplace and a huge family room off of the kitchen.  The primary suite has a terrific view of the pool area, two large walk-in closets and high ceilings.  The primary bath features a separate shower, dual vanities & ample storage. All bedrooms have access to their own bathroom!  The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, modern white cabinetry and granite countertops.  The large breakfast bar opens out to the eat in kitchen area and family room, perfect for entertaining.  Upstairs the possibilities are endless with two additional bedrooms, two full baths and a large loft area, perfect as a second den or homework area.  Out back, you walk into your own personal resort.  Large curvilinear pool with screened enclosure, tropical landscaping with privacy hedges and stamped concrete patio for relaxing or entertaining.  Hot water heater 2020, A/C's 2020 & 2022, huge 3 car garage, manual storm shutters and long paver driveway round out the highlights.  Located in the heart of Port St. Lucie and Tradition, this opportunity provides a fantastic location not far from gorgeous beaches, shopping and quick access to highways.  Please make sure to check out the 3D virtual walk through and schedule an appointment today!
